    "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 417.4, 566.776, 452.524 ],
    "font" : "THSarabunPSK",
    "font size" : 14.04,
    "text color" : "[0.0]",
    "content" : "Preparation of the establishment before accepting cooperative education students perform planning and setting procedures, detailed as follows:"
  }, {
    "type" : "list",
    "pdfua_tag" : "L",
    "id" : 26,
    "level" : "1",
    "page number" : 4,
    "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 80.874, 567.055, 413.044 ],
    "numbering style" : "arabic numbers",
    "number of list items" : 5,
    "list items" : [ {
      "type" : "list item",
      "pdfua_tag" : "LI",
      "page number" : 4,
      "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 338.18, 566.749, 413.044 ],
      "font" : "THSarabunPSK",
      "font size" : 14.04,
      "text color" : "[0.0]",
      "content" : "1. Planning for the admission of cooperative education students. Establishment should hold a meeting between the administrators, personnel staff and head of the student admissions department. In which all departments may write on the topic of the work that students to perform and the reviewer to consider before giving the head of the department to the school to announce to the students.",
      "kids" : [ ]
    }, {
      "type" : "list item",
      "pdfua_tag" : "LI",
      "page number" : 4,
      "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 298.58, 566.583, 333.824 ],
      "font" : "THSarabunPSK",
      "font size" : 14.04,
      "text color" : "[0.0]",
      "content" : "2. The establishment should allocate budget and resources such as compensation, welfare, equipment, tools and appliances suitable for the performance of students. And is safe for the performance of students, etc.",
      "kids" : [ ]
    }, {
      "type" : "list item",
      "pdfua_tag" : "LI",
      "page number" : 4,
      "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 239.18, 566.794, 294.224 ],
      "font" : "THSarabunPSK",
      "font size" : 14.04,
      "text color" : "[0.0]",
      "content" : "3. The head of the department who wants to accept students to work must assign personnel in the department to act as supervisors. The supervisor must have sufficient time for counseling and operation to be completed regarded as the workload given by the establishment to perform the same as regular work.",
      "kids" : [ ]
    }, {
      "type" : "list item",
      "pdfua_tag" : "LI",
      "page number" : 4,
      "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 140.15, 567.055, 234.824 ],
      "font" : "THSarabunPSK",
      "font size" : 14.04,
      "text color" : "[0.0]",
      "content" : "4. The job description that is suitable for the performance of cooperative education should be a job that cooperative students can complete within the time. Should not beyond the ability of a student to do the actual job maybe a job at the planned workplace. But those who work still do not have time to work. The developer should plan and set a time frame for students to work as scheduled.",
      "kids" : [ ]
    }, {
      "type" : "list item",
      "pdfua_tag" : "LI",
      "page number" : 4,
      "bounding box" : [ 72.024, 80.874, 566.633, 135.914 ],
      "font" : "THSarabunPSK",
      "font size" : 14.04,
      "text color" : "[0.0]",
      "content" : "5. Supervisor at the establishment and the person responsible for the operation Cooperative education work should jointly consider the selection of students who notify their intention from the educational institution. By selecting students who are qualified for the job description or project topic set by the establishment.",
      "kids" : [ ]
    } ]
